mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Americana: Dakota Land", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Overseas Dateline", "Style Series: Star Thru", "Caller of the Month: Al Berry", "Paging the Roundancers: Lloyd and Maizie Poole", "'Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Square Dance Organization Handbook", "On the Record and Record Report", and "Experimental Lab: Pass the Buck (Pass the Doe)".
